abstract: City of Winnipeg, Manitoba, is giddy over the return of its NHL hockey Jets after an absence of 15 years when the franchise moved away.
snippet: After an absence of 15 years, the Winnipeg Jets return to life Sunday afternoon. Which is a good thing because the emotions sweeping the citizens of this prairie city have grown to a fever pitch.
